# CYB213 Midterm - Socket & Port Scanner

Contains:
- `server.py` — multi-client TCP server (default 127.0.0.1:9000)
- `client.py` — simple TCP client
- `port_scanner.py` — threaded port scanner (safe targets only: 127.0.0.1, scanme.nmap.org)

Run examples:
- `python3 server.py --host 127.0.0.1 --port 9000`
- `python3 client.py --host 127.0.0.1 --port 9000`
- `python3 port_scanner.py 127.0.0.1 -p 22,80,443`

See /screenshots for demonstration evidence and timestamps.

Academic integrity and reflection included in `reflection.txt`.
